{{!-- Upper header content on homepage --}}
<h1>{{title}}</h1>
<div class="missionStatement">
    <p>Our concept is simple: The World can be hard. It can knock you down and sometimes you can’t find you way back
        onto your feet.
        <br>At {{title}}, at your fingertips are the words and powerful emotions of mankind’s most inspirational
        speakers, influencers and humanitarians.
        <br>They’re all here with one mission: to Inspire you, to motivate you, and to remind you of the power of words
        and the compassion of the human spirit.</p>

    <p>That’s not all -- you’ll be able to connect with people from around the world and share your own inspirations.
        <br>Not a wordsmith? No problem, simply send some of your favorite quotes to help people through the tough
        times. Because remember:</p>
</div>
<p class="homeQuote">“You cannot do a kindness too soon, for you never know how soon it will be too late.”
    <br>-Ralph Waldo Emerson, American Author</p>

{{!-- The ask, directs to below buttons --}}
<p class="howQuestion">How are you feeling today? Choose one below:</p>

{{!-- Contains the emojis, texts and buttons associated with user feelings --}}
<div class="emotionContainer">
    <div class="columnOne">
    <div class="columnOneText">
        {{#each feeling}}
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary emotionText" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#exampleModal" id="{{_id}}">{{name}}</button>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="columnTwo">
        <div class="columnTwoImage">

    </div>
    </div>
</div>
        
<div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">{{speaker}}</h5>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      {{#each quote}}
      <div class="popup {{feeling}}">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">"{{content}}"</h5>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <p>{{speaker}}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
        <button type="button" class="shuffle btn btn-primary">Shuffle</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Save this quote</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

